\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/gwiCmS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/gwiCmS</a><br />\n<br />\npls pin thx"},{"pid":"bb41ec76cb4979de9228ccc0da784783aa6ab9fb","tid":2342899,"uid":43150,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8a2850a4efa60b2b176d85001abb561e8f97548a","tid":2342899,"uid":154486,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T13:13:23.000Z","msg":"<p class=\"center\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">冠絕東方<br />\nNulli&nbsp;secundus&nbsp;in&nbsp;Oriente</span><br />\n</span></p>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T13:43:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n義勇無雙 冠絕東方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"818419d4c0dfbc8421457b263c8d747f4062fc98","tid":2342899,"uid":49974,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T13:45:58.000Z","msg":"大家熟識的「巴斯光年」鄧梓峰便是該軍團的末代軍人。<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce41f6a0c31f7b7434db2966ec00508351fc65d7","tid":2342899,"uid":191588,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T13:47:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"413bf1b6a91b3a9b8adda7d368da54e312350e36","tid":2342899,"uid":43150,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"818419d4c0dfbc8421457b263c8d747f4062fc98","tid":2342899,"uid":49974,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T13:45:58.000Z","msg":"大家熟識的「巴斯光年」鄧梓峰便是該軍團的末代軍人。<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T13:57:22.000Z","msg":"冇錯，佢係皇家香港義勇軍中尉<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.watershedhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/RHKR_鄧梓峰-1024x896.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.watershedhk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F09%2FRHKR_%E9%84%A7%E6%A2%93%E5%B3%B0-1024x896.jpg&h=950a3874&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n//皇家香港軍團（義勇軍）始創於1854年，由於克里米亞戰爭需要抽調駐港皇家海軍，香港政府徵召志願市民組成防衛隊。1878年，義勇軍經重組後，成為本港一支常設志願軍團。軍團起初由歐藉人士組成，1920年代開始招募本地華人。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>義勇軍於1941年香港保衛戰中力戰到底，1957年獲頒「Hong Kong」戰役榮銜（Battle Honour），繡於軍旗上。1970年，軍團獲英女王御賜「皇家」之名</strong>。翌年，軍團獲頒一面英式騎兵（偵察部隊）燕尾式軍旗。<br />\n<br />\n1984年中英簽署《聯合聲明》，隨後義勇軍「另起爐灶」及合併警察的方案均被否決，不能過渡九七。1995年9月2日下午，義勇軍舉行解散前列隊巡遊，行經灣仔會展，由首任華人布政司陳方安生女士檢閱，向市民道別。9月2日晚上，義勇軍於粉嶺新圍兵房舉行解散大會操，由末代港督彭定康檢閱。9月3日，義勇軍光榮解散。//<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.watershedhk.com/royalhongkonregiment-disbandment-1993/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.watershedhk.com%2Froyalhongkonregiment-disbandment-1993%2F&d=sZqGLlkYYIxatccyfr7NWFiy1AgKJyIubMvfhItfpFI%3D&h=2755435f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.watershedhk.com/royalhongkonregiment-disbandment-1993/</a>"},{"pid":"359007011743ba2881460c7f8b4822cfac4d1fb8","tid":2342899,"uid":132175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T14:03:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9360383e5492a54a88e799ddf04bbfa3a90a6956","tid":2342899,"uid":223428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T14:04:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae05e03743d6cde616e2a95279c46f4407d449dc","tid":2342899,"uid":303977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T14:04:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bf2e30850bf08ec7491d299ccffcc13e557d7413","tid":2342899,"uid":49974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"413bf1b6a91b3a9b8adda7d